# Agent Types

This document defines the types of agents in the platform.

---

## 🤖 Orchestrator Agent

- Controls workflow
- Decides which API to call
- Coordinates multiple agents

---

## ⚙️ Task Agent

- Executes specific tasks
- Calls APIs
- Returns results

---

## 🔍 Retrieval Agent

- Fetches data
- Queries APIs/services
- Provides context to other agents

---

## 🔄 Interaction Flow

User → Orchestrator → Task Agent → API → Service
